snippet.title: Facebook Horizon | New Worlds in the Making
snippet.description:
Welcome to Horizon, a social experience where you can explore, play and create in extraordinary ways. In Horizon, you’re not just a visitor. You’re part of what makes it great. 
 
Horizon is currently an invite-only beta. Sign up now to apply.
